{"tid":353841,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"零裝備跳過樓","createTime":"2017-08-10T03:00:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-10T05:22:01.000Z","uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c1845139f71a479d69d1a2453559b2926f3bc492","tid":353841,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T03:00:53.000Z","msg":"英國一名玩街頭極限運動的Freerunner，突破保安阻撓，一個前空翻「樓過樓」，「飛越」寬闊空隙到大廈另一邊。<br />\n<br />\nYouTube片段顯示，身無裝備、只穿短褲跑鞋的恩尼斯（Greg Ennis），在倫敦中部歷史悠久的Somerset House外，從馬路起跑，按着圍牆頂一躍，打個空翻，飛越闊得令人「心離一離」的空隙，在大樓另一邊着陸。<br />\n<br />\n保安員叫也叫恩尼斯不住。途人見到他起跳，都為之驚訝，有人見他成功在「對岸」着陸，拍掌讚他有膽色。<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20117359&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170810\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20117359%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170810&d=cms4Z2pWDrUixDO0cdo5%2FP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=87574fa8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20117359%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170810&h=16b3ad1b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20117359&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170810</a>"},{"pid":"c61b9ec66e1f5066fb854e7d400fd7abd2f71125","tid":353841,"uid":38456,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T03:02:10.000Z","msg":"抄展鵬"},{"pid":"4a812e066e834fc94ca99b74da15c85568fb8698","tid":353841,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T04:13:17.000Z","msg":"呵依！"},{"pid":"78a81cbf2f6603902908933844376e7ab2409b52","tid":353841,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T05:22:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>抄展鵬</blockquote><br />\n關正傑呀"}]}